  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5652689/" class="title-link">温暖的共鸣</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5652689"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/hilaryzx/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1056338-5.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/hilaryzx/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">hilaryzx</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-11-13"
      class="main-meta">2012-11-13 14:53:46</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5652689_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  读这本书，是在一个月前去拉萨的火车上，对铺的姑娘借给我的。读过一部分之后，还在火车上，我就在本子上写下了这段感想：  对面借给我一本《最好的时光在路上》。该书的作者不愧是旅游杂志记者和编辑出身，文字很了得，感情很细腻。其实关于旅行的文字，由于写的是个人的经历...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">4有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5652689_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5652689_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










            <p class="pl" align="right">
                &gt;
                <a href="reviews">
                    更多书评164篇
                </a>
            </p>
</section>
    
